objects.blogDescription: What is in a blog? A blog (short for “weblog”) is an online journal or informational website run by an individual, group, or corporation that offers regularly updated content (blog post) about a topic. It presents information in reverse chronological order and it's written in an informal or conversational style.
objects.author: Himanshu
